### 5. No CORS Policy (OWASP A05: Security Misconfiguration)

Without explicit CORS headers, browser-based cross-origin requests are either completely blocked or, if misconfigured later, completely open.

**Fix:** Define an explicit allowlist:

```js
const cors = require('cors');
app.use(cors({
  origin: ['https://yourdomain.com'],
  methods: ['GET', 'POST'],
  allowedHeaders: ['Authorization', 'Content-Type'],
}));
```

